escription:"Track your favorites pools",faq:"Frequently Asked Questions",faqTrialQuestion:"How does the free trial work?",faqTrialAnswer:"When you connect your wallet for the first time, you automatically get 4 days of free premium access. No credit card required.",faqCancelQuestion:"Can I cancel anytime?",faqCancelAnswer:"Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time. You'll continue to have access until the end of your billing period.",faqPaymentQuestion:"What payment methods do you accept?",faqPaymentAnswer:"We accept payments in USDC and other major cryptocurrencies. All transactions are processed securely on-chain.",faqRefundQuestion:"Do you offer refunds?",faqRefundAnswer:"We offer a full refund within the first 7 days of your subscription if you're not satisfied with our service.",explore:"Explore",limitOrders:"Limit orders",portfolio:"Portfolio",login:"Login",logout:"Logout",feedback:"Feedback",language:"Language",languageSettings:"Language Settings",numberFormat:"Number Format",english:"English",spanish:"Spanish",usFormat:"US Format",esFormat:"European Format",connectWallet:"Connect Wallet",securityVerification:"Security Verification",verifyingHuman:"Verifying you're human...",pleaseWait:"Please wait while we complete the security check",completeVerification:"Complete Verification",completingVerification:"Completing verification...",termsAgreement:"By connecting a wallet, you agree to our Terms of Service",noWalletDetected:"No wallets detected",sendFeedback:"Send Feedback",feedbackSent:"Feedback sent!",reportIssue:"Report Issue",tellUsThink:"Tell us what you think...",issue:"Issue",missingPool:"Missing Pool",missingCoin:"Missing Coin",wrongData:"Wrong Data",other:"Other",address:"Address",chain:"Chain",pairLabel:"Pair Label",coinName:"Coin Name",symbol:"Symbol",url:"URL",poolUrl:"Pool URL",explanation:"Explanation",description:"Description",submitIssue:"Submit Issue",sendFeedbackBtn:"Send Feedback",explorePools:"Explore Liquidity Pools",explorePoolsDesc